  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to prove the findings of a preliminary study which strongly
      suggest the hypothesis that the result of conventional embolectomy for acute, severe
      lower-limb ischemia can be improved by controlled reperfusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
